                    "value": "<p>The target can’t recover from the fatigued condition caused by black apoxia until the disease is cured;</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"24\" data-pf2-traits=\"disease\" data-pf2-label=\"Black Apoxia DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span>;</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> carrier with no ill effect (1 day);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Fatigued]{Fatigued} (1 day);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 2} and fatigued (1 day);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> dead</p>"
